 big screen. Get tickets NOW.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-17T17:30:29.000Z"},{"id":"6942ca4c3e076467442dc374","key":"_FEOCxb6gC0","name":"Official Trailer 2","site":"YouTube","size":2160,"type":"Trailer","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-17T14:30:05.000Z"},{"id":"6942b369b438b17b0b7a2c4e","key":"cgGKUN5x6ZI","name":"Everything’s on the line.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-16T17:30:00.000Z"},{"id":"69413758d5db940074f0ded6","key":"UGBHWvH4yTQ","name":"A new world. A new mission.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-15T18:10:13.000Z"},{"id":"693d9e7fa011253a2283e743","key":"iRH5Aw7jvkc","name":"Official Clip 'Chutes and Ladders’","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Clip","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-09T20:13:31.000Z"},{"id":"69381805cc491dae4a63854a","key":"689hSIk0gsY","name":"Forward is the only way.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-08T18:00:08.000Z"},{"id":"6931d8de6025a82bf0f91443","key":"2Xnl9_uJxJc","name":"Get to the crater.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-04T18:02:14.000Z"},{"id":"6930a4c573f73718c46ee234","key":"W_OTmtikAJE","name":"Official Clip - ‘Fragment Strike’","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Clip","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","published_at":"2025-12-03T19:59:59.000Z"},{"id":"6929c6ce4779d992ddd9d49c","key":"BdFoswul4_0","name":"This Thanksgiving, don't fight with your family — fight for your family.","site":"YouTube","size":1080,"type":"Teaser","official":true,"iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","publishe